public class UsesOccurrenceReference
extends _UsesOccurrenceReference
    This reference uses a special UsesOccurrenceForeignKey to uniquely identify a UsesOccurrence for the purpose of associating it to PathOccurrences.

    Use the newUsesOccurrenceReference static factory method(s), not the UsesOccurrenceReference constructor, to construct instances of this class. Instances must be constructed using the static factory(s), in order to ensure proper initialization of the instance.
